Brian Tee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Tee 0 Jaebeom Takata (born March 15, 1977), known professionally as Brian Tee, is a Korean Japanese American actor best known for his role as D.K. (also known as The Drift King) in the action film The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift (2006) and as Dr. Ethan Choi in the NBC medical drama Chicago Med (2015–present).
